ultra_amplified_dimension.amplified_port:
A portal block to enter and exit Ultra Amplified Dimension!

 Right click the block without crouching to teleport.




 To make this portal, you need to make a portal frame in the following pattern:

Top Layer
CTC
TTT
CTC

Middle Layer:
AAA
ADA
AAA

Bottom Layer:
CBC
BBB
CBC

D = Polished Diorite
A = air space
C = Polished Granite
T = Top Polished Andesite Slab
B = Bottom Polished Andesite Slab

NOTE: C, T, and B may be different blocks if the UA config for them was changed.
